General.Name: Dignitana AB
General.Description: Dignitana AB (publ), a medical technology company, develops, produces, and markets medical cooling devices in the United States and internationally. It offers DigniCap, a scalp cooling system used to reduce hair loss from certain chemotherapy treatments, as well as in the treatment of breast cancer. The company was incorporated in 2007 is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
